metadata.description: GGMetasex is the first NFT to offer an experience where you can access the GGMansion and GGMetasex virtually as well as physically. Accessible only to Shareholders. By owning the GGMetasex Gold NFT not only will you get direct access to the mansion physically as well as the virutal MetaSex metaverse, but you will also be eligible to profit from the GGMansion's live stream income.
